{"title":"Wilde Bicycle Co Lightweight Waypoint Gravel Fork","link":"https://theradavist.com/wilde-waypoint-gravel-fork/","date":1709570846000,"content":"<p>Wilde launches a new lightweight carbon gravel fork, the <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=0cc5823d-633e-4665-9b9e-f9b62fb1ab4d&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wildebikes.com%2Fcollections%2Ffrontpage%2Fproducts%2Fwaypoint-carbon-fork-tapered\" target=\"_blank\">Waypoint</a>. At 478g with an uncut steerer, it is among the lightest fully featured carbon forks on the market. Available to consumers, bike shops, and to other small framebuilders and bike companies…<span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"5472\" height=\"3648\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Waypoint5.jpg?fit=1200,3648&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Waypoint5.jpg?w=5472&amp;quality=75 5472w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Waypoint5.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Waypoint5.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Waypoint5.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Waypoint5.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Waypoint5.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"5472\" height=\"3648\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Waypoint9.jpg?fit=1200,3648&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Waypoint9.jpg?w=5472&amp;quality=75 5472w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Waypoint9.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Waypoint9.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Waypoint9.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Waypoint9.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Waypoint9.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Meet the Wilde Waypoint. At 478g with an uncut steerer, it’s among the lightest fully featured forks on the market and was designed with rider comfort and durability in mind. The fork legs were specifically engineered to soak up bumps and isolate the rider from road chatter, allowing you to go longer and in greater comfort, without sacrificing strength or durability.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"5472\" height=\"3648\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Waypoint3.jpg?fit=1200,3648&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Waypoint3.jpg?w=5472&amp;quality=75 5472w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Waypoint3.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Waypoint3.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Waypoint3.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Waypoint3.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Waypoint3.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><em>The Waypoint was designed for bikes with an EC34/44 or straight 44mm headtube that take a tapered steerer. If you need a fork for a standard straight 1 1/8″ steerer or EC34 headtube, the original <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=0cc5823d-633e-4665-9b9e-f9b62fb1ab4d&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wildebikes.com%2Fcollections%2Ffrontpage%2Fproducts%2Fwayfinder-fork\" target=\"_blank\">Wayfinder fork</a> is the one you want.</em></p>\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Three Pack Mounts</li>\n<li>Flat Mount Brake</li>\n<li>Thru Axle – 12x100mm</li>\n<li>Internal Brake Routing</li>\n<li>Internal Dynamo Routing</li>\n<li>Fender Mounts</li>\n<li>Fully Threaded Center Mount</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Specs</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fork Weight: 478g with uncut steerer</li>\n<li>Tire Clearance: 700c X 2.1″ or 27.5″ X 2.3″</li>\n<li>Axle to Crown – 398mm</li>\n<li>Rake – 49mm</li>\n<li>Steerer – 350mm length, Taper 1.125″ to 1.5″</li>\n<li>Spacing – 100mm</li>\n<li>Axle Length – 130mm 12 x 1.5</li>\n<li>Compatible Rotor Size – 140mm and 160mm</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Capacity</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Three Pack Mount – 6 lbs per side</li>\n<li>Rack – 20 lbs</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=0cc5823d-633e-4665-9b9e-f9b62fb1ab4d&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wildebikes.com%2Fcollections%2Ffrontpage%2Fproducts%2Fwaypoint-carbon-fork-tapered\" target=\"_blank\">Wilde Bicycle Co</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/wilde-waypoint-gravel-fork/\">Wilde Bicycle Co Lightweight Waypoint Gravel Fork</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"0712be95c5b6d907086cf408faff8487a411d4b12a52d95532c9d1b2db8a2837","category":"Cycling"}